I"F<ul>
  <li>Champion the creation of people-centered designs by considering customer feedback, metrics, usability findings, market analysis, and other research</li>
  <li>Create flows, wireframes, visual mockups, and simple prototypes</li>
  <li>Build and maintain detailed user interface specifications and design patterns</li>
  <li>Present design work to the user experience team for review and feedback</li>
  <li>Partner with development teams to build experiences: provide red-lines, create assets, and review finished interfaces</li>
</ul>

<p>To be successful, this designer will possess an exceptional eye for detail and embrace a highly iterative approach to design. Additionally, this designer must possess the communication skills to persuasively convey proposals and specifications to other teams within the organization.</p>
